brainrotfilter (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Ported from pfSense/FreeBSD to Linux (Debian/Ubuntu)
  * Replaced pfctl with conntrack for connection killing
  * Replaced SSH-based pfSense configurator with local Linux configurator
  * Uses openssl for CA certificate generation
  * Uses iptables for transparent proxy and QUIC blocking
  * Systemd service integration
  * Web-based setup wizard for Linux

 -- IAmDestructoman <github@destructoman.dev>  Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
